00064 /*****************************************************************************\

00066  * ------------------------------------------------------------------------- *
00067  * Mspec links to Pcode, Hcode, and Lcode modules.  In order to allow this   *
00068  * to take place without requiring front-end modules to link to liblcode.a,  *
00069  * Mspec code is divided into two classes as follows:                        *
00070  *  - mi_*.c must not depend on linkage to liblcode.a                        *
00071  *  - ml_*.c may depend on linkage to liblcode.a                             *
00072 \*****************************************************************************/

00087 enum
00088 {
00089   M_IM_LCODE = 1000,            /* Lcode instr set, impact macros,
00090                                    impact calling convention, impact
00091                                    stack layout, etc. */
00092 
00093   /* The rest of these models are for internal use only!  -ITI (JCG) 2/99 */
00094   M_IM_VER_1,                   /* Lcode instr set, impact macros,
00095                                    impact calling convention, impact
00096                                    stack layout, etc. */
00097   M_IM_HP_LCODE,                /* Lcode instr set, hp macros,
00098                                    hp calling convenction, hp stack
00099                                    layout, etc. */
00100   M_IM_HP_MCODE,                /* hppa PA-RISC instr set, hp macros,
00101                                    hp calling convention, hp stack
00102                                    layout, etc. */
00103   M_IM_SPARC_LCODE,             /* Lcode instr set, sparc macros,
00104                                    sparc calling convention, sparc
00105                                    stack layout, etc. */
00106   M_IM_SPARC_MCODE              /* sparc instr set, sparc macros,
00107                                    sparc calling convention, sparc
00108                                    stack layout, etc */
00109 };
